  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Explosive Energy Weapon",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "爆炸性能量武器",
    "TraditionalChinese": "爆炸能量武器"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">high-energy weapon</span> attachment for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool</span>. The Neutron Cannon energises atmospheric particles before propelling them towards hostile targets, delivering <span class=\"name name-stellar\">significant area damage</span><br><br>Access fire mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>. Charge the weapon with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>, then release to unleash a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">volley of ionised particles</span>.<br><br>While the cannon can deliver instantaneous single shots, <span class=\"name name-technology\">longer charges</span> will result in significant increases to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">speed and volume of released particles</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>设计的<span class=\"name name-technology\">高能武器</span>组件。中子大炮通过发射高能大气悬浮颗粒对敌对目标造成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大量范围伤害</span><br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>激活开火模式。按<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>为武器充能，松开后即可施放<span class=\"name name-stellar\">一连串离子颗粒</span>。<br><br>中子大炮可以随时发射单枚投射物，不过<span class=\"name name-technology\">持续充能</span>能够显著提高<span class=\"name name-technology\">投射粒子的速度与数量</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">工具組</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高能量武器</span>配件。中子砲會將大氣粒子充能後，向敵對目標推進，造成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">重大區域傷害</span><br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 進入開火模式。按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 替武器充能，放開後即可釋放<span class=\"name name-stellar\">電離粒子群</span>。<br><br>雖然大砲可瞬間單發射擊，但<span class=\"name name-technology\">較長的充能時間</span>會顯著增加<span class=\"name name-technology\">釋放粒子的速度和數量</span>。"
  },
